            "tests": [
                {
                    "id": "upstream_default_scenario_all_reaction_rates",
                    "description": "Pins all 20 output diagnostics (R1-R17, L_CH4, P_HCHO, P_O3_gross) at the canonical upstream test scenario — every input species and rate constant at its declared default (CH₄=4.5e19, OH=1e12, CH₃O₂=1e14, NO=2.5e15, NO₂=2.5e16, O₂=5.25e24, M=2.5e25, …; the input_vals Dict reused across GasChem.jl test/test_methane_oxidation.jl). This single test reproduces and tightens eight upstream MethaneOxidation testitems at rel=1e-10: `Table 6.1 Rate Constants` (test_methane_oxidation.jl:66-96 — implicit: every R is a rate constant × concentrations, so a wrong rate-constant default shifts a pinned R off its value), `Reaction Rate R1 (CH4+OH)` (lines 124-150, upstream R1≈2.874e11 rtol=0.02 — the exact-Arrhenius value pinned here, 285468004462.3754, agrees to 0.67%), `Reaction Rate R3 (CH3O2+NO)` (lines 152-177, upstream R3≈1.925e12 rtol=0.01 — reproduced exactly at 1.925e12), `HCHO Production (P_HCHO = R6 + R8)` (lines 179-209 — P_HCHO, R6, R8 all pinned: 99751899999999.98 = 99749999999999.98 + 1900000000.0), `CH4 Loss Equals R1` (lines 211-233 — L_CH4 and R1 both pinned to the same value 285468004462.3754), `Net O3 Production (P_O3_gross = R15 + R3)` (lines 235-261 — P_O3_gross, R15, R3 pinned: 3950000000000.0 = 2025000000000.0 + 1925000000000.0), `Oxidation Chain Relative Rates` (lines 266-290, upstream R3>R4>R5 and R3/R4>10 — reproduced structurally: pinned R3=1.925e12 > R4=5.2e10 > R5=3.5e9, R3/R4≈37.0), and `HCHO as Key Intermediate` (lines 292-318, upstream R10,R11,R12>0 and R12>R11 — reproduced: pinned R12=4e11 > R11=3e11). Also reproduces the upstream `All Reaction Rates Positive` testitem (lines 376-409) since every one of the 20 pinned values is positive, and the `CH4 Lifetime` testitem (lines 347-374, upstream ≈4.96 yr rtol=0.1) since the pinned L_CH4 gives CH₄/L_CH4 = 4.5e19/285468004462.3754 ≈ 5.00 yr.",
                    "parameter_overrides": {},
                    "time_span": {
                        "start": 0.0,
                        "end": 1.0
                    },
                    "assertions": [
                        {
                            "variable": "R1",
                            "time": 0.0,
                            "expected": 285468004462.3754
                        },
                        {
                            "variable": "R2",
                            "time": 0.0,
                            "expected": 1.3125000000000003e+18
                        },
                        {
                            "variable": "R3",
                            "time": 0.0,
                            "expected": 1925000000000.0
                        },
                        {
                            "variable": "R4",
                            "time": 0.0,
                            "expected": 51999999999.99999
                        },
                        {
                            "variable": "R5",
                            "time": 0.0,
                            "expected": 3500000000.0000005
                        },
                        {
                            "variable": "R6",
                            "time": 0.0,
                            "expected": 99749999999999.98
                        },
                        {
                            "variable": "R7",
                            "time": 0.0,
                            "expected": 7043285735.348479
                        },
                        {
                            "variable": "R8",
                            "time": 0.0,
                            "expected": 1900000000.0
                        },
                        {
